#%RAML 1.0 SecurityScheme
type: Basic Authentication
description: API Supports Client ID policy applied as Basic Authentication of HTTP Headers.
describedBy:
   headers:
     Authorization:
       description: The Authorization header must be derived as client_id:client_secret - encoded to Base64
       type: string
       example: "Basic 7bc7af29041645fe80aa5d16e71876e5="
